ets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收聲啦，屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n壓力大睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1391a9ab66238528c66e2d75eec5f0a1563b11e","tid":379160,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祖樂比未執之前我都覺得好食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家開返我覺得好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係執淨環球個間，依家先再開分店"},{"pid":"8180c509449f97c4834231a90262a30a33c0ec9a","tid":379160,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"Wendy's 仲正呀 屌你"},{"pid":"2ec76086025e37885e0e015e0be1a4617f3de603","tid":379160,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但真係好食wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢未執個時都話好食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係記得以果陣既物價黎講都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1e05ad23036e9488848913dfa7b5f52b19f8d7","tid":379160,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但真係好食wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢未執個時都話好食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係記得以果陣既物價黎講都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貴少少, 但係唔係貴好多. 同麥當勞相比俾貴20%左右. <br />\n20%睇落個數好大, 其實係20蚊同25蚊分別, 到執嗰期係25蚊同35蚊咁上下, 但係質素上高過麥當勞好多."},{"pid":"f69f5204a0b36d1fed1d26fd83e744af49039999","tid":379160,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"因間真係重開，30/40一個餐，班連燈仔就話咁貴不如食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前m記都高質過依加好多平好多啦，下下揾十年前比有咩意思"},{"pid":"30e2aa1bd7d0ae62616fc6f420e43cae491883b1","tid":379160,"uid":9391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"哈敵C好食呀"}]}